Figure 7 depicts the change in supply chain profit caused by demand disturbance. The variation diagram of the total profit of the supply chain disturbed by demand is still composed of a piecewise function. It can be seen from the figure that with the increase in demand disturbance value, the profit of the supply chain is increasing.Fig. 7
Effect of Δa\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
